{"tid":2195852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多家傳媒拍得吳文遠警車內被毆 事隔近3年監警會同意警無過錯","createTime":"2020-09-09T12:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T03:11:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8da0f263d7370e02b30ad8a201fee43461532895","tid":2195852,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"社民連秘書長吳文遠於2017年七一早上示威時遭警員帶上警車毆打，過程被傳媒拍下。吳事後即就被毆打、粗言穢語辱罵等情況向投訴警察課投訴，事隔近3年，警方通知大部份指控均「無法證實」，而「濫用職權」指控更列作「並無過錯」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/HPAOYCBG3JAH3K2LX7R53KI4TQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FHPAOYCBG3JAH3K2LX7R53KI4TQ%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=dfca2e58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200909%2FHPAOYCBG3JAH3K2LX7R53KI4TQ%2F&h=935da16a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200909/HPAOYCBG3JAH3K2LX7R53KI4TQ/</a>"},{"pid":"87e4e52f032f8ea97018325bc8b180ee7a5e7549","tid":2195852,"uid":183844,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:13:01.000Z","msg":"作為死黑警，直情係表現優良添"},{"pid":"e723d5fb27cbf8430d1389aad6702a84f4f6e045","tid":2195852,"uid":53666,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:14:17.000Z","msg":"黑警：唔射瓜你係皇恩浩盪"},{"pid":"59def9160dc48fcc31e7f52b1a37353cb3383f5a","tid":2195852,"uid":114074,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:16:23.000Z","msg":"作為盡忠職守嘅黑警<br />\n用私刑梗係無錯啦"},{"pid":"39b60693426aac8445119798f141e8ecddf44220","tid":2195852,"uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:23:34.000Z","msg":"監狗會連狗公廁都不如，大case一定砌唔入，細case就扮砌得入去做數"},{"pid":"184b975c122b12365397f5bcc51d221f0c559ec5","tid":2195852,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"你有無見過老鼠偷嘢食因為咬爛左個袋而認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces